# Static marketing pages (/, /keyring, /registry, /docs/agents) are served as
# ASSETS by Cloudflare Pages BEFORE this rule; every other path falls through to
# the React SPA served AT /index.html.
#
# CRITICAL — do NOT point the SPA fallback at a named .html file (e.g. /app.html).
# Cloudflare Pages rewrites any rule whose destination is a .html asset to its
# "pretty URL": /app.html becomes a 301 to /app, which drops the requested path
# and breaks every SPA route (this took the site down once). /index.html is the
# canonical shell and has no pretty-URL redirect, so it is the ONLY safe target.

# Signup is retired — the web door is /start on the console.
/signup            https://app.basedagents.ai/start   301

# Generic alias for the sandbox recovery page (codex.html is served as an asset
# at /codex ahead of these rules). Destination is the pretty URL, NEVER the
# .html asset — see the warning above.
/sandbox           /codex                              301

# Everything not served as a static asset is the React SPA.
/*                 /index.html                          200
